Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like this building?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a cool place or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're special, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Those ugly dogs in my fan\Nclub don't know about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:01:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're disgusting, you vulgar,\Narrogant, retarded celebrity punk...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because you have some TV show.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shame--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like being kicked\Nby a retarded celebrity punk?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You old bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.39,0:01:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Your stinking perfume makes me sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the disgusting one, bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.50,0:01:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to sue you for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My son is an excellent lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A punk like you will\Nbe squashed like a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hear me, punk?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We found traces of two bullets...\Nin the chest and in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see signs of blood under the skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have died instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Akai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It must have been a very special gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The bullets exploded inside his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Better check those bullet fragments.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the medical team here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all in the hospital\Nbecause of food poisoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Those assholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What a waste of our tax money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with granny?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably shocked to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it was a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Get an autopsy just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this guy's a celebrity?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He has seven TV shows a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a popular comedian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,His usual material is about corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's gonna laugh at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What a tearjerker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He was such a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why would anyone kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the nicest guy I ever knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand breaking\Nup our team like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ogata at the studio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:05:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,His outraged fans are\Nrushing to the location.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We can see how popular he was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, according to our sources,\Nthis case may involve organized crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for that old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,People die everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in the mood today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I have enough problems already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:05:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Be more punctual, Oburi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We've called someone else in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You take care of the one in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The other one will take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What did they do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of them are child molesters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to pay for what they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another one besides me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this weekend again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me when you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You know our usual activity...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife just isn't\Ngood enough, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The reward for each\Nadult is the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it from Kanie later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You stink, Mr. Akai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oburi, I don't have\Nan easy job, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The stink from the corpses\Nmakes my eyes water all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And that rotten smell is so strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder I always stink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Akai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think about what I asked you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hold you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your generosity makes me feel weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...you have to take\Ncare of three more jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's between you and me, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to be fair to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Kanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kanie, I'll do my best to be on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You retard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy, give us the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You got my jacket dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't that nice, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home and wash it yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,1 05 yen is your change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You look good in that uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be a new flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked Kanie\Nwhere I worked part-time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,As in ''the sand you can't hold''\Nand ''the feather blown by the wind.''
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.60,0:14:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oburi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Oburi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How much do you know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanie told me your name, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Oburi your real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very unusual name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone says that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a family?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're alike, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Akai to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...my guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strange coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...we have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Those earrings\Nmust be very special to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You were wearing\Nthem the last time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They look weird, yet really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...made from the\Nblood of my papa and mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of my lucky charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a Hollywood movie star, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of my classmates are fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't know that\Nhe had a twin brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be here in a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the third celebrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...the right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get the wrong one, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He has three bodyguards, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do I get him?
